{"id":"api/core/Signal","title":"Signal","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/Signal\", \"name\": \"Signal\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/signals/src/api.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L22-L41\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/signals/src/api.ts#L22-L41\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"signal\">Signal<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Signal#signal\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"This API is in Developer Preview\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">developer preview</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">通知消費者任何更改的反應值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A reactive value which notifies consumers of any changes.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/Signal#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;T&gt; = (() =&gt; T) &amp; {\n    [SIGNAL]: unknown;\n};\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Signal#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">訊號是返回其當前值的函式。要存取訊號的當前值，請呼叫它。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Signals are functions which returns their current value. To access the current value of a signal,\ncall it.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可以使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">signal</a></code> 函式將普通值轉換為 <code><a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a></code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Ordinary values can be turned into <code><a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a></code>s with the <code><a href=\"api/core/signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">signal</a></code> function.</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/WritableSignal\n - api/core/computed\n - api/core/isSignal\n - api/core/rxjs-interop\n - api/core/rxjs-interop/toObservable\n - api/core/rxjs-interop/toSignal\n - api/core/signal\n - guide/rxjs-interop\n - guide/signals\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Signal#description\n - api/core/Signal#signal\n - api/core/signal\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/signals/src/api.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L22-L41\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/signals/src/api.ts#L22-L41\n-->"}